<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Avil Page (apache maven)</title><link>http://www.avilpage.com</link><description></description><atom:link href="http://www.avilpage.com/categories/apache-maven.xml" type="application/rss+xml" rel="self"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Jan 2017 17:52:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>https://getnikola.com/</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>How To Install Maven On Ubuntu?</title><link>http://www.avilpage.com/2014/05/how-to-install-maven-on-ubuntu.html</link><dc:creator>Chillar Anand</dc:creator><description>&lt;div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on"&gt;&lt;h3 style="text-align: left;"&gt;What Is Maven?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;quote&gt;" Maven is a build automation tool used primarily for Java projects. Maven addresses two aspects of building software: First, it describes how software is built, and second, it describes its dependencies. "&lt;/quote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Apache Maven describes it as: &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;quote&gt;"Apache Maven is a software project management and comprehension tool. Based on the concept of a project object model (POM), Maven can manage a project's build, reporting and documentation from a central piece of information."&lt;/quote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 style="text-align: left;"&gt;Install Maven On Ubuntu:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;Installing Maven is quite easy. Just copy &amp;amp; paste the following commands.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;code class="bash hljs " style="background-color: #333333; border-bottom-left-radius: 6px; border-bottom-right-radius: 6px; border-top-left-radius: 6px; border-top-right-radius: 6px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.298039) 0px 1px 2px inset, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392) 0px 1px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498039) 0px -1px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; padding: 8px; position: relative; white-space: pre;"&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: transparent; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #eeeeee;"&gt;sudo apt-get update&lt;br class="Apple-interchange-newline"&gt;sudo apt-get install maven&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style="-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: black; font-family: monospace; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;It will take a while(~ 50Mb) to download it.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;To check whether you have  successfully installed or not type this to get the version of Maven.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;code class="bash hljs " style="background-color: #333333; border-bottom-left-radius: 6px; border-bottom-right-radius: 6px; border-top-left-radius: 6px; border-top-right-radius: 6px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.298039) 0px 1px 2px inset, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392) 0px 1px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498039) 0px -1px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; padding: 8px; position: relative; white-space: pre;"&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: transparent; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #eeeeee;"&gt; mvn -v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: transparent; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #eeeeee;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;I just took some screenshots with maven installed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4utzKh991VA/U3jfOlwESUI/AAAAAAAAKeU/nEc_DofEUC4/s1600/install-maven-ubuntu-4.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4utzKh991VA/U3jfOlwESUI/AAAAAAAAKeU/nEc_DofEUC4/s1600/install-maven-ubuntu-4.png" height="58" width="640"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7WYEI0hzvGs/U3jfOgFGy5I/AAAAAAAAKec/ohHHhCb0dqc/s1600/install-maven-ubuntu-5.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7WYEI0hzvGs/U3jfOgFGy5I/AAAAAAAAKec/ohHHhCb0dqc/s1600/install-maven-ubuntu-5.png" height="58" width="640"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-P3Nv5_L_fRE/U3jfOtqY1FI/AAAAAAAAKeY/XlKOYhXcmKc/s1600/install-maven-ubuntu-6.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-P3Nv5_L_fRE/U3jfOtqY1FI/AAAAAAAAKeY/XlKOYhXcmKc/s1600/install-maven-ubuntu-6.png" height="158" width="640"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you want dive into Maven, grab this free e-book &lt;a href="http://www.sonatype.com/books/mvnref-book/reference/" target="_blank"&gt;"Maven - The Complete Reference " by O'Brien.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>apache maven</category><category>apache maven tutorial</category><category>how to apache maven</category><category>how to ubuntu</category><category>install maven ubuntu</category><category>maven free ebook</category><category>tech</category><guid>http://www.avilpage.com/2014/05/how-to-install-maven-on-ubuntu.html</guid><pubDate>Sun, 18 May 2014 16:35:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>